<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Current_Privilege_Level" title="Current Privilege Level" class="mw-redirect">Current Privilege Level</a> (<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CPL0" title="CPL0" class="mw-redirect">CPL0</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CPL1" title="CPL1" class="mw-redirect">CPL1</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CPL2" title="CPL2" class="mw-redirect">CPL2</a>, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CPL3_(x86)" title="CPL3 (x86)" class="mw-redirect">CPL3</a> on x86 CPUs)</li>
